{
  "stem": "12674.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I came home every night, and I had a decent bed to sleep in and whatever food there was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- I was living at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- if you live for all the time in a place, you have ways of get-- getting more food than they allow you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we didn't eat like we had eaten before, but I never went hungry, not once.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Instead of eating, I don't know, veal cutlet, I might be eating a piece of fish, if it was available, or-- or-- or somebody had a chicken, or-- some-- some [INAUDIBLE] you-- you took a piece of jewelry and-- and bought yourself a goose someplace or-- if you have lived in a place all your life, you have-- there are ways of knowing what to do and where to go and-- everything.",
      "word_count": 72
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews were dogs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not allowed to sit on park benches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not allowed to go to movies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were not allowed to use public transportation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were not allowed to go to swimming pools.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not allowed to go to theaters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They got smaller ration cards than other people-- lesser portions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Other people got clothing cards, you know, for clothing, coupons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Jews did not get that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Jews were required to turn in all their jewelry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was ashamed because people-- everybody was doing what-- nobody ever said-- we didn't know, in our beleaguered little thing there, that what went down in the rest of the world.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I never, until after-- way after the war, when I found out that there was a resistance here or this was there, Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I never heard of anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
